name: 赤城 - Akagi Azur Lane LORA. / 赤城 (アズールレーン)
description:
New Version is OUT.

READ ABOUT THIS VERSION AT RIGHT BOTTOM CORNER + CLICK SHOW MORE.

You can now request a Character's LORA. CLICK HERE

Posting my first Lora Release, never seen a Lora on Akagi or much IA Art on Akagi, so i created one.

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Trained on 350-450+ Images with Good quality. (SFW + NFSW)

AnimeFullFinalPruned Used when trained.

Update: Added some images, Yandere Akagi Style! (Kl-F8-anime2 Vae needed, otherwise i use OrangeMix Vae!)

Weight: Recommended: 0.6-1 - Best Result: 0.8-1.

See Grid image examples for Weights comparison (Abyss Model): https://i.imgur.com/HZaVmT8.png

Model used: AbyssOrangeMix2_hard, YesMix, Corneo's 7th Heaven mix, MeinaMix

But probably works with any Anime Model.

He can do the base Default skin Pretty well, Other are not 100% precise but he can do it somewhat if you describe it good. (See examples images)

Default, Swimsuit, Wine version.

Trigger words is in the prompt image examples.

Just the basic for really Activating Akagi Lora is AkagiV4, but you need to describe a little bit for Best Result, like in the Image examples.

Negative Embedding used: EasyNegative, BadPrompt2.

PS: I have other Lora that doesn't exist anywhere that i created too like Shimakaze, Kaga or Anime Lora Like Denji but in Chainsaw Mode! I will probably post it Later.

Share you're image in Comments :).

modelVersions.name: V5
modelVersions.description:
New Version AkagiV5, Largely Superior to older Ver.

  • Trained on 768x Resolution for Maximum Detail & Quality.

  • 244 Images+ All are Original Art from Artist ONLY 4K Images, at the Best Quality possible, that i sorted Manually. (SFW+NFSW)

  • Lower datasets for more Detail & Precision on Official Skin & Other Skin.

  • Pruned tags, so you just need to describe it a little, Like in prompts example.

  • More Flexible than Older Ver.

  • Probably Work's with Realistic Model's.

  • Work's with any Anime model & Add Detail Tweaker Lora.
